    Welcome to OSR Clinics in Ontario

    OSR Clinics is an Ontario-based psychotherapy and mental health group offering therapy, qEEG-guided neurofeedback, and evidence-based treatment for ADHD, PTSD, anxiety, and depression.

    Assessing ADHD

    At OSR Clinics in Ontario, we offer in-depth ADHD assessments conducted by experienced professionals who consider all aspects of your or your child’s behaviours, challenges, and strengths.

    If you suspect that you or your child may have ADHD, it’s essential to go beyond quick online checklists. While they can provide a glimpse into potential symptoms, they’re not enough to diagnose ADHD accurately.

    Read More

    Individual Therapy

    At OSR Clinics, our individual therapy services offer compassionate support for managing anxiety, depression, trauma, life transitions, and personal growth.

     

    Whether you're navigating a difficult change, seeking mental health support, or looking to better understand yourself, our skilled counselors provide a safe space for healing and resilience-building tailored to your unique needs.

    Read More

    Neurofeedback

    At OSR Clinics, we specialize in science-backed QEEG-guided neurofeedback, a non-invasive approach designed to retrain the brain for optimal function.

     

    Whether you're navigating ADHD, burnout, high-pressure performance demands, or communication delays in children, our personalized approach delivers measurable change.

    Read More
